### Create student (valid)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/add-student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Shifa A. Zafar",
  "email": "shifa@example.com",
  "course": "Computer Science"
}

### Missing/short name (invalid)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/add-student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Al",
  "email": "al@example.com",
  "course": "IT"
}

### Duplicate email (invalid after first request)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/add-student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Another User",
  "email": "shifa@example.com",
  "course": "IT"
}
